                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4806" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1212</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9413 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谁击碎了瑞幸梦想：做空使然还是风险注定？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Whether shorting or risks to hinder Luckin Coffee’s success</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谭吉玉，刘高常，安琪琪，朱文兴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">瑞幸咖啡</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新零售；战略管理；风险管理；瑞幸咖啡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">new retail; strategic management; ERM; Luckin Coffee Inc.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了瑞幸咖啡新零售模式发展历程的光环锦簇与荆棘丛生。发展初期，瑞幸咖啡无疑是幸运的，凭借快速上市、快速扩张、快速烧钱的商业模式、“门店+快取店+外卖厨房”的业务融合生态系统，一步步走向辉煌。然而，幸运之神似乎并没有陪伴瑞幸太久，做空机构浑水发布的一份做空报告，直指瑞幸财务造假，把中概股以及瑞幸公司推向全球性年度丑闻风口，制造了互联网经济前所未有的尴尬。瑞幸怎么了？瑞幸路在何方？值得深思。通过对案例多角度展示和分析，培养学员战略双轮驱动意识。一方面，帮助学员认知新零售的原始商业生态和潜在风险，能根据现有风险管理理论进行战略情景规划，从风险角度思考瑞幸失败的成因；另一方面，让学生熟悉利用财务数据识别盈利模式缺陷。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case described the development process of Luckin Coffee’s new retailing with halos and embarrassments. At the early stage of development, Luckin Coffee Inc is undoubtedly lucky. With the business model of rapid listing, rapid expanding and high burn rate for consumers, as well as the business integration ecosystem of “physical store &amp; pick-up store &amp; takeout kitchen”, Luckin Coffee has gradually becomes brilliant. However, fortune didn’t seem to accompany Luckin for a long time. A short report issued by Muddy Waters, a short-seller, accused Luckin of financial frauds, which pushed Chinese concept stocks and Luckin Coffee to the center of an annual global scandal, and created an unprecedented embarrassment for the Internet economy. It&#39;s worth thinking about Luckin Coffee how to cope with that and to find the way out. From many angles to display and analysis of this case, it helps students to understand the adjustment of strategic management and the original business ecology of the new retail, to think about how to help the enterprises overcome the difficulties according to the existing theories, and initially form enterprise-wide risk management thinking. Meanwhile, students are expected to understand audit due diligence, with which cultivate students&#39; observation and insight, and establish correct ethics.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险管理和盈利模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
